capiko-ai optionally configures Headroom's MCP server into the GitHub Copilot CLI
environment it manages (writing an entry into ~/.copilot/mcp-config.json that runs
`headroom mcp serve`). capiko-ai does not include, link against, modify, or
redistribute any Headroom source code or binaries — the user installs Headroom
themselves. This NOTICE is provided as attribution for that integration.

